MORA TSP SCNARIO 3.2.2 CHANGING CORE ASSIGNMENT OF PARTITIONS

In this scenario the partitions the cores are shared with different cores, itâ€™s like each core having an
individual schedule.

        25ms | 25ms | 25ms | 25ms | 25ms | 25ms | 25ms | 25ms | 25ms | 25ms |
Core0 | <------ P0 ------> | <P3> | <--- P5 --> | <P0> |      | <P0> | <P2> |
Core1 | <------ P2 ------> |             | <--- P4 --> |      | <--- P3 --> |
Core2 |                                                                     |
Core3 |                                                                     |

P0 - IO
P1 - Mission Manager
P2 - Thermal Control
P3 - Power Control
P4 - AOCS
P5 - Payload


Partitions P2, P3, and P5 need to define CONFIGURE_MAXIMUM_SEMAPHORES in rtems_config.h after configure.
Ex: #define CONFIGURE_MAXIMUM_SEMAPHORES 1
